		<div class="entry-content"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/09/09/today-in-small-business-best-and-worst-cities-for-hispanic-entrepreneurs/" data-title="Today in Small Business: Best and Worst Cities for Hispanic Entrepreneurs" data-description="Why operating cash flow is more important than net profit. Can gas pumps be smart?">
				<div class="ad sharetools-inline-article-ad"></div>
				<div id="MiddleLeft" class="ad middle-left-ad nocontent robots-nocontent"></div>
				</div><div class="inlineModule"><div class="entry"><h6 class="kicker"><a href="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/category/dashboard/">Dashboard</a></h6><p class="summary">A daily roundup of small-business developments.</p></div></div>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Whatâs affecting me, my clients and other small-business owners today.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>The Economy</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The Conference Boardâs <a href="//247wallst.com/economy/2014/09/08/employment-trends-index-looks-better-than-labor-department-payrolls-data/?">Employment Trends Index</a> increased in August and was up 6.4 percent compared with a year ago.</li>
<li>Consumer credit <a href="//www.businessweek.com/news/2014-09-08/consumer-credit-in-u-dot-s-dot-surges-on-more-loans-for-automobiles">surges on</a> more loans for automobiles.</li>
<li>Weak incomes and savings are the reason <a href="//blogs.wsj.com/economics/2014/09/08/why-more-renters-arent-buying-hint-weak-incomes-savings/?">renters</a> arenât buying.</li>
<li>Fracking is spurring a <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/09/09/business/an-energy-boom-lifts-the-heartland.html?_r=0">Rust Belt rebound</a> in manufacturing.</li>
<li>McDonald&#8217;s <a href="//www.marketwatch.com/story/mcdonalds-sales-woes-continue-in-august-2014-09-09-84855351">sales woes continue</a>.</li>
<li>Here&#8217;s the case for trying to fix the economy by <a href="//www.vox.com/2014/9/9/6122517/helicopter-drop-money-print-fed-blyth-lonergan">printing more money</a>.</li>
<li>The dollar is <a href="//qz.com/261759/the-result-of-years-of-relentless-fed-money-printing-a-strenthening-dollar/">getting stronger</a>.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Entrepreneurship</strong></p>
<ul>
<ul>
<li>WalletHub has released a list of the best and worst cities for <a href="//wallethub.com/edu/best-and-worst-cities-for-hispanic-entrepreneurs/6491/">Hispanic entrepreneurs</a>.</li>
<li>Six <a href="//m.bizjournals.com/philadelphia/print-edition/2014/08/08/six-minority-business-owners-share-the-insights.html">minority business owners</a> from the Philadelphia area talk about how and why they started their businesses.</li>
<li>Only a few hundred of the roughly 10,000 s<a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/09/09/nyregion/black-women-find-a-growing-business-opportunity-care-for-their-hair.html">tores that sell hair products</a> like relaxers, curl creams, wigs and hair weaves to black women are owned by African-Americans.</li>
<li>The <a href="//nymag.com/news/features/martine-rothblatt-transgender-ceo/?u">highest paid</a> female executive in America was born male.</li>
</ul>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span id="more-88442"></span></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Start-Up</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Here&#8217;s how <a href="//articles.bplans.com/start-successful-restaurant-guide/?u">to start</a> a successful restaurant.</li>
<li>World Startup Events is a wiki <a href="//thenextweb.com/insider/2014/09/08/world-startup-events-helps-find-key-networking-tech-events-across-globe/?">guide to networking and tech events</a> across the globe.</li>
<li>Many start-ups are using Google Hangouts in their <a href="//www.washingtonpost.com/business/on-it/start-ups-using-google-hangouts-in-broader-search-for-tech-talent/2014/09/07/26cd6c58-339c-11e4-8f02-03c644b2d7d0_story.html">broader search</a> for tech talent.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Finance</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>PayPal <a href="//www.fastcompany.com/3035430/fast-feed/paypal-finally-embraces-bitcoin?partner=rss">is embracing</a> Bitcoin.</li>
<li>Shake Shack <a href="//www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-09-04/shake-shack-said-to-aim-for-1-billion-ipo-valuation.html">is aiming</a> for a $1 billion initial public offering valuation.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Cash Flow</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="//dharmawat.blogspot.com/2014/09/why-operating-cash-flow-is-more.html">Operating cash flow</a> is more important than net profit.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Employees</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/09/08/us/legal-use-of-marijuana-clashes-with-workplace-drug-testing.html">legal use of marijuana</a> can conflict with employer rules.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Management</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Kareem Abdul-Jabbar says <a href="//time.com/3296175/bruce-levenson-atlanta-hawks-racist-email-kareem-abdul-jabbar/">the owner of the Atlanta Hawks isn&#8217;t a racist</a>; he&#8217;s a businessman.</li>
<li>The chief executive of Hertz <a href="//news.yahoo.com/hertz-ceo-steps-down-accounting-errors-171037280--finance.html">steps down</a> after a series of accounting errors.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Marketing</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>For $100, Olive Garden&#8217;s <a href="//money.cnn.com/2014/09/08/news/companies/olive-garden-pasta/index.html">Never Ending Pasta Pass</a> will let customers eat nonstop for seven weeks.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Ideas</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A start-up wants the gas pumps of the future <a href="//upstart.bizjournals.com/companies/startups/2014/09/08/can-gas-pumps-be-smart-this-startup-thinks-so.html">to be connected</a> to the Internet and let drivers do things like pay parking tickets and renew vehicle registrations.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Strategy</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Whole Foods <a href="//mashable.com/2014/09/08/whole-foods-instacart-delivery/#:">partners with</a> Instacart to offer one-hour deliveries.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Around the Country</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A Kentucky columnist wants a <a href="//www.kentucky.com/2014/09/08/3417850_dave-cooper-locally-brewed-drink.html?sp=/99/349/&amp;rh=1">locally brewed drink</a> to be more available in area franchises.</li>
<li>The <a href="//www.wsav.com/story/26475374/small-business-confidence-level-dips-in-northeast-ohio">confidence level</a> of small businesses dips in Northeast Ohio.</li>
<li>Illinois officials are <a href="//www.wbez.org/news/illinois-begins-accepting-applications-marijuana-businesses-110764">accepting</a> applications for people who want to open a medical marijuana dispensary or cultivation center.</li>
<li>The insurance company Aon estimates that the <a href="//www.insurancejournal.com/news/national/2014/09/08/339847.htm">economic losses</a> from the recent quake in the Napa Valley and floods in other parts of the country will top $4 billion.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Social Media</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Facebook videos <a href="//www.fastcompany.com/3035399/fast-feed/facebook-videos-hit-1-billion-daily-views">hit one billion</a> daily views.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Taxes</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The Obama administration <a href="//www.foxbusiness.com/markets/2014/09/08/lew-treasury-will-act-in-very-near-future-to-make-corporate-overseas-shifts/">will decide</a> &#8220;in the very near future&#8221; what actions it can take to make it less profitable for American companies to shift their legal addresses to other countries.</li>
<li>These are the <a href="//digital.accountingtoday.com/accountingtoday/sr_top_100_most_influential_people#pg2">most influential people</a> in tax and accounting.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Online</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>An ex-Google employee shares <a href="//www.wired.com/2014/09/metanautix/">his big-data</a> secrets.</li>
<li>In case you were too embarrassed to ask, <a href="//www.nytimes.com/video/business/international/100000002865514/what-is-alibaba.html">this video explains what Alibaba does</a>.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Technology</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Apple is <a href="//bits.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/09/09/apple-live-blog-new-iphone/?_php=true&amp;_type=blogs&amp;ref=business&amp;_r=0">expected to announce</a> two new iPhones and a smartwatch.</li>
<li>Amazon <a href="//techcrunch.com/2014/09/08/amazon-dumps-the-fire-phone-down-to-99-cents/?ncid=rss">drops the price</a> of its smartphone to 99 cents.</li>
<li>TiVo unveils a <a href="//bostonherald.com/business/media_marketing/2014/09/tivo_unveils_crazy_huge_5000_dvr_with_enough_storage_for_three">$5,000 DVR</a> with enough storage for three years of TV.</li>
<li>Microsoft <a href="//www.businessinsider.com/microsoft-finally-rolls-out-delve-2014-9">rolls out</a> a product that will help Office 365 users manage their lives.</li>
<li>Someone will make a wearable device for these <a href="//www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/iPad/Apple+Smartwatch/feature.asp?c=61396">seven parts of the body</a>.</li>
</ul>
